>> time required: 20 minutes
>> course: entre

In #mortar add @black mustard seed{0.5%tsp}, minced seeded @green chili{2%tbs}, @coconut{2%tbs}, and @salt{0.5%tsp} make paste
In small pan add @ghee{1%tbsp}, add @black mustard seed{0.25%tsp} until they start popping
Add @curry leaves{5} and the above curry paste, and minced @ginger{1%tbsp}
Cook for a few minutes then add @turmeric{1%pinch} and chopped @banana{1} and fry for ~{30%seconds}
Turn heat to very low and add @yogurt{1.5%cups}
Let cool
